递归解决子问题。

```python
class Solution:
    def hasPathSum(self, root: TreeNode, sum: int) -> bool:
        if root == None:
            return False
        if root.left == None and root.right == None:
            return sum == root.val
        if root.left and self.hasPathSum(root.left, sum - root.val):
            return True
        if root.right and self.hasPathSum(root.right, sum - root.val):
            return True
        return False
```
